    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my favorite ride and it's honestly been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained, making it the perfect reliable companion for your daily commutes or weekend getaways. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next big adventure with you! Drop me a message if you'd like to come see it!",
