    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies. Power is delivered to the rear wheels via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been reinforced, and the VANOS unit has been overhauled to ensure timing reliability. The suspension geometry is maintained with upgraded polyurethane bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, preserving the chassis's neutral handling characteristics. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with spirited use, the mechanical vitals are excellent, backed by a recent valve adjustment and a consistent compression test across all six cylinders.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained engine. Clean title. Minor cosmetic wear. Runs well.",
