      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera 2 is a mechanically sound example of Porsche\u2019s water-cooled evolution. Powered by the 3.6L M96 flat-six, it features a 6-speed manual transaxle with a short-throw kit for crisp gear engagement. The IMS bearing and rear main seal have been proactively serviced, mitigating common failure points. It sits on a refreshed suspension with Bilstein B6 dampers, maintaining the factory\u2019s precise turn-in and high-speed stability. Equipped with four-piston monoblock calipers and cross-drilled rotors, the braking system offers consistent thermal management and pedal feel. This is a driver\u2019s car with a solid service history and uncompromising performance.",
